{"tid":541552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"空姐涉偷Aeon 2.2萬元嬰兒用品","createTime":"2018-01-26T14:21:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T15:53:33.000Z","uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0d546b7a9b6b816757b4e12d3e633c1ec58447af","tid":541552,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T14:21:51.000Z","msg":"空姐涉偷Aeon 2.2萬元嬰兒用品<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】家住半山的空姐，涉於去年在鰂魚涌永旺百貨（Aeon）偷竊大量嬰兒用品，包括13包尿片、20個奶樽等，總值達2.2萬元，案件昨於東區法院提堂。控罪指出，被告曾寶琪（32歲）於去年12月12日在鰂魚涌永旺百貨偷竊20個嬰兒奶樽、13包尿片、10盒「樂高（Lego）」玩具、7瓶嬰兒奶樽清潔劑、7包嬰兒專用清潔棉、5包嬰兒廁紙、3支體溫計、3個嬰兒理髮器、2個母乳儲存袋、2件嬰兒揹帶、2支兒童電動牙刷、2瓶兒童維他命、2個濾水器、1個貯物袋、1條支撐帶、1個毛氈袋，以及1個奶粉盒等物品。<br />\n<br />\n包括13包尿片20奶樽 3月再訊<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至3月8日再訊，以待索取法律意見，被告准以1.5萬元保釋。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號︰ESCC234/18】"},{"pid":"2e8110e44b0090baf928b7f190ef723fd48bf537","tid":541552,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T14:22:19.000Z","msg":"Sorry 無圖"},{"pid":"711407425aaeb5d03e3aae5499679f0b213e1a37","tid":541552,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e8110e44b0090baf928b7f190ef723fd48bf537","tid":541552,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T14:22:19.000Z","msg":"Sorry 無圖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T14:24:28.000Z","msg":"有冇link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cc3bc313c0377df1d080fc06685942a30982ea8","tid":541552,"uid":12720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T14:30:14.000Z","msg":"點偷咁多???用GIP?"},{"pid":"1fbf025bb7c266043dc2af3c25c2e64d6f40d70c","tid":541552,"uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"711407425aaeb5d03e3aae5499679f0b213e1a37","tid":541552,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e8110e44b0090baf928b7f190ef723fd48bf537","tid":541552,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":2,"